Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:02.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm really late again
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.07,0:01:13.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多半得开除我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.07,0:01:13.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe they'll finally fire me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.90,0:01:16.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:16.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.47,0:01:17.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:17.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Locked?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.15,0:01:19.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't happening
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.05,0:01:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.95,0:01:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horror--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:30.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1194,480)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.77,0:01:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's unspeakable
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you see, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:27.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's closed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.79,0:01:30.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王关门了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.79,0:01:30.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab is closed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.06,0:01:32.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说我白起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:32.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean I got out of bed for nothing?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The doors are locked--
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门锁上了  我们却在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the doors are locked and we are on the outside
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门外汉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Outsiders
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么办才好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:38.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.07,0:01:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡在里面多么寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There are Krabby Patties inside all alone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.45,0:01:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站一边去  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just stand aside, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.07,0:01:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来开锁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and let me unlock the door
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, you're here
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们担心你有啥三长两短
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.10,0:01:51.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we were worried something might have happened to you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.59,0:01:54.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世间顶级美食差点就不复存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when the world would've been deprived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.05,0:01:54.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the greatest food known to man
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你害我钥匙掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made me drop me keys
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.88,0:01:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也给点私人空间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me some space, lad
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,螃蟹就不能有点空间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't a crab get a little space?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太狠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Harsh
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.86,0:02:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老背
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.86,0:02:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me back
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你伤着了吗  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  我就单纯忍痛弯个腰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just doubled over in pain
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,强忍泪水不哭出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.89,0:02:12.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fighting back tears in me eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近就流行这种舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because it's a new dance craze
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  还以为你伤着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, I thought you were hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.04,0:02:17.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是伤着了  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:17.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am hurt, you idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉吼你了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I snapped at you, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是我的背真的疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just me back is killing me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪我的高低不平旧床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me old lumpy mattress--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,睡上去就好像睡破珊瑚一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's like trying to sleep on broken coral
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快把我给逼疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.55,0:02:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going out of me mind
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老背
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:30.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me back
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该怎么办  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:35.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,办什么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why do anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢蟹老板现在这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:37.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like the new Mr. Krabs--
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更爱吼你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he yells at you more
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没开玩笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也没
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:42.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So am I
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要给他买个新床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should get him a new mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给他来个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and surprise him with it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.19,0:02:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我们就再也不会晚上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then we'll never have to be late to work again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.99,0:02:49.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:49.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是想要我把血汗钱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You want me to spend my hard-earned money
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.59,0:02:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花在比我还富的小气老板身上是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on my richer-than-me skinflint boss?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免谈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没关系  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:02:59.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你等下一定会接受这提议的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll warm up to the idea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你跟我来  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming with me, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我老想去床垫专卖店了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I always wanted to go to a mattress store
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(554,658)}床垫专卖店
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来没见过这么多床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen so many mattresses
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:14.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得店里有几张床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How many do you think there are?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ten
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cool
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's plenty more than that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试睡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try 'em out--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找找有没有看中的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,find one you like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:54.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,450)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you morons doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给蟹老板做贺卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Making a card for Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟新买的床垫一起送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.15,0:04:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To go with his new mattress
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,130)}睡个安稳觉
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,懂了  原来你是想拍老板马屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:09.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see, you're just kissing up to the boss
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,显得我态度很难看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to make me look bad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't stand for it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贺卡给我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that card
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想耍小聪明赢过我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trying to outsmart me, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  我给咱仨都签了名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.51,0:04:19.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, I signed it for all of us
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都没出钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't even help pay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板高兴就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As long as Mr. Krabs is happy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的老背
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me back
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正肯定又睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here goes another useless attempt
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但也只能睡我这高低不平大床垫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to sleep on me mountainous, lumpy mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's queer--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,床垫感觉特别舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me mattress seems strangely cozy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.20,0:04:41.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:41.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,butter
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.02,0:04:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.97,0:04:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界末日了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Armageddon
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.64,0:04:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.97,0:04:50.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:50.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.88,0:04:51.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.88,0:04:51.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们来我卧室干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What in a blue-eyed scallop are you doing in me bedroom?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We noticed
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你睡在高低不平旧床垫特别难受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how miserable you were on your lumpy, old mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就提议给你买个新的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I suggested we get you a new one
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是你提议的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought it was your idea
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我旧床垫哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, where's me old mattress then?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也亲自处理好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I took care of that personally, too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经拖去垃圾场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had it hauled away to the dump
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.48,0:05:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:12.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱都在那床垫里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:15.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,money was in that mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就没听说过银行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever heard of a bank?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:26.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.17,0:05:29.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还要给你送贺卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:29.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And we got you a card
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面有钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there money in it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:37.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,676)}急诊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,严重吗  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it serious, Doctor?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will Mr. Krabs be all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板得了金钱昏迷症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is in a cash-coma
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有钱物归原主了才能脱离生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:44.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the return of his money can save his life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was SpongeBob's fault
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是他提议要给蟹老板买床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:48.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Getting Mr. Krabs a new mattress was his idea
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.92,0:05:49.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:49.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别急
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not so fast
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这贺卡上面写着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This card says
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我提议的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:54.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"This was all my idea
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱你的章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Love, Squidward"
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是蟹老板没康复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If Mr. Krabs doesn't pull through
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就得去坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're going to jail
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新床垫你买的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did this, SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.24,0:06:05.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你没去垃圾场找回蟹老板的床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:05.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you don't get Mr. Krabs' mattress back from the dump
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就要宰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am going to mur
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再亲自帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:11.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help you do it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真的很在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He really does care
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:16.39,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(698,456)}垃圾场
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a dump
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(878,330)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定得进去  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:19.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to get in there, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板就指望我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is counting on us
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  那边那个是要找的床垫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, isn't that the mattress over there?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Terrific, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.83,0:06:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you found it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.65,0:06:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.92,0:06:26.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:26.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.32,0:06:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那边  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over there, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那个特大看门虫底下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:31.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,underneath that really big guard worm
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That figures
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:38.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这位没医保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This man has no insurance
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对住不起这间病房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll never be able to afford this room
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.82,0:06:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  护士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, nurse
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把病人赶到走廊去  快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Extract the patient to the hallway, stat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,294)}汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:49.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,214)}零食
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个确定就是蟹老板的床垫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's Mr. Krabs' mattress all right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起夺回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go get it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  下面是计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, here's the plan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个静悄悄地潜进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You two quietly go in there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从看门虫底下挪走床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,remove the mattress out from under the guard worm
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.47,0:07:02.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能  把虫子吵醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:02.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without "waking the worm"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吵醒就不礼貌了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because that would be rude, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾场的虫子最凶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And nothing's meaner than a junkyard worm
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它会生吃了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll eat you alive
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.98,0:07:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有最重要的任务在身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got the most important job
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得要放哨保安全
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:17.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to keep watch to make sure it's safe
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就谢了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My pleasure
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's get a move on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很美啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it beautiful, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐这里风景尽收眼底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can see everything from up here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you morons doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这边好像可以看到我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, I think I can see our houses from here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't see 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.17,0:07:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's do it again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们俩白痴干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you idiots do?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你进去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, what are you doing in there?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该放哨的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:52.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to keep watch
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  而且你还吵醒看门虫了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:54.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and you woke up the guard worm, too
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你们吵醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You blockheads woke
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:07:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.73,0:08:00.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:00.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,worm
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Doctor?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.35,0:08:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:07.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有关你的病人  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Regarding your patient, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有如下结论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have come to this conclusion
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  请说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:11.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, go on
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须特地把他挪开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have to surgically remove him out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让他挡了糖果贩卖机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from in front of the candy machine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:19.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,264)}零食
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样我才买得到坚果棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can get to the Nutty-Nut Bar
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.20,0:08:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,护士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nurse
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫饵呼叫寻垫者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:31.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worm Bait to Retriever
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫饵呼叫寻垫者  我们进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Worm Bait to Retriever, we're in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.10,0:08:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,寻垫者呼叫虫饵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Retriever to Worm Bait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,待在里面  别出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stay in, don't go out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:37.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Understood
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.17,0:08:37.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:37.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:37.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(718,920)}出 去
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  待着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.37,0:08:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Understood
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.50,0:08:39.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:39.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们在垃圾场另一头是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're on the far side of the dump, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Affirmative
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  那就大吵大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, then make lots of noise
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,引走看门虫  让它离开床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to draw the guard worm away from the mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方便我寻回床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so I can retrieve it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.21,0:08:48.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:48.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Affirmative
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:49.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Out
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪不得他会自称寻垫者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's why he calls himself the Retriever
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要叫虫饵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are we called Worm Bait?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.26,0:08:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是好办法  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:01.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great idea, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的完美计划太顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And my perfect plan falls into place
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.81,0:09:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像知道我们代号为什么叫虫饵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I know why our code name is Worm Bait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.64,0:09:20.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫子乖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:20.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice worm
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫子温柔点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:23.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, kind, gentle worm
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  它喜欢你的木头勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:31.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, SpongeBob, he likes your wooden spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think you're right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看它玩不玩捡棍子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See if he plays catch
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好棍子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See the stick, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get it, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前方安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coast is clear
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你真是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squiddy, you are a genius
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:46.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我正好很需要木头勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I needed a wooden spoon
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.56,0:09:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放屁股口袋保管  省得弄坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll just keep it safe from harm in my back pocket
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来搬床垫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now for the mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早该猜到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have guessed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  医生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.92,0:10:03.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Doctor
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船骸管理员  有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Administrator Flotsam, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我注意到你的病人蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It has come to my attention that your patient, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在门口的人行道昏迷不醒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is out on the front sidewalk
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.38,0:10:10.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:10.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.80,0:10:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想什么乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking, man?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是做生意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're trying to run a business here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能把病人留在人行道上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't leave patients on the sidewalk
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not to worry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,护士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.47,0:10:18.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nurse
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.00,0:10:18.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:18.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个怎么磨蹭这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you two, hat's the holdup?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉自己很傻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We feel silly
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  要为蟹老板着想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, do it for old man Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能再解释一遍计划吗  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you explain the plan again, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  但首先
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, but first
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个古龙水擦一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,put on this cologne
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(836,842)}牛排酱
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牛排酱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Steak sauce?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你们两个扮成了精切牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, so you two are dressed as choice cuts
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进去喊一声  不给糖就捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.87,0:10:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You go in there and yell "Trick or treat"
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.38,0:10:50.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虫子会发现自己忘了囤万圣节糖果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The worm will realize
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:50.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he forgot to stock up on Halloween candy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会去补货  然后床垫到手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll leave to buy some, then we take the mattress
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,古龙水给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that cologne
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:57.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get in there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万圣节快乐  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Halloween, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次绝对伤不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am not going to get hurt this time
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那不是蟹老板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那条看门虫好像不太高兴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That guard worm doesn't look very happy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跑  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清醒过来赶紧跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run like you're not in a coma
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.67,0:11:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.67,0:11:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,me money
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, money
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发誓再也不丢下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll never leave you alone again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's us
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不给糖就捣蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Trick or treat
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都没认出你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.42,0:11:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't recognize you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话说你们干嘛要打扮成肉排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:38.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, why are you two dressed as meat?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不只是肉排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:40.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not just meat--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是精切牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're choice cuts
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:42.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:44.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I give up
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.94,0:11:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get away
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.60,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(153,262)}老板打官司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(253.316,442)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.52,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(453.678,662)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(407.566,442)\frz29.52}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:57.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(529.736,692)\frz29.08}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:04.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(254,700)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又过了一个不眠夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And so passes another sleepless night
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.75,0:12:18.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连个蟹黄堡都偷不到  烦得我睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,haunted by my inability
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:18.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to steal even a single Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能今天就能偷到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe today will be the day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.07,0:12:24.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的客气话  电脑老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:24.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronizing words, computer wife
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有没有计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you even have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:30.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(824,204)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要什么计划
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plan, schman--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.00,0:12:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我直接临场发挥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to wing it
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况还能糟到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.94,0:12:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's the worst thing that could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,402)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was easy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许今天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe today is the day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.36,0:12:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能偷到蟹黄堡的秘密配方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to steal the Krabby Patty formula
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:44.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Careful, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边地板刚拖过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:45.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just mopped there
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.11,0:12:48.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.11,0:12:48.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at you, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又万分悲惨地摔在地上失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once again you've fallen flat on your back
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没能偷到我的秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:54.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in another pathetic attempt to steal me formula
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尽管你试了又试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Though you tried and tried
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.17,0:13:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果我的美味秘方还是到不了你嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:59.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you haven't had the smallest nibble
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of my delicious formula
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后也不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you never will
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.91,0:13:07.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明知自己都这么废了  怎么睡得着觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you sleep at night
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,knowing you're a complete failure?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该放个小心地滑警告牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There really should be a "Wet Floor" sign
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.77,0:13:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  要是那边滑倒的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.77,0:13:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if that were me who slipped
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.92,0:13:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就去把老螃蟹告个倾家荡产了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd sue old man Krabs for all he's got
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡秘方是不是也能告过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:18.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that include the Krabby Patty formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疼死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pain
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手臂还有腿都没知觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't feel my arms and legs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像都摔断了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think they're broken
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要打官司赔偿我的痛苦和折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:31.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to sue for my pain and suffering
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打官司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sue?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像伤得很重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks bad
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小家伙真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:35.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor little man
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold up a second
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.09,0:13:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种小事还是别闹到法庭上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:41.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we don't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,drag this little incident into court, do we?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.71,0:13:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把蟹黄堡秘方交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you transfer the Krabby Patty formula to me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就不计较你讨人厌的过失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll forget your gross negligence
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无赖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Scoundrel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要我秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have my formula
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等我没命了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when you pry it from me lifeless claws
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法庭见了  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See you in court, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,疼死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The pain
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.49,0:14:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,简直疼得要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The deep frying pain
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我废了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in a blue ruin
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会不惜一切代价
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will do whatever it takes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保护蟹黄堡秘方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep the Krusty Krab formula
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不让它落入痞老板的魔掌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:15.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from getting into Plankton's evil hands
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我真正需要的是好律师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I really need is a good lawyer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  有谁说律师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:19.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, did somebody say "lawyer"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(934,280)}理查德臭鱼烂虾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1084,618)}律师
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是理查德臭鱼烂虾  一名律师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:21.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Richard A Bottomfeeder, Attorney At Law
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无意间注意到了刚刚的卑鄙情节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but notice that despicable display
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.91,0:14:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请律师要花多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how much is this going to cost me?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实官司打输不收钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:29.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I won't charge you a dime unless we win
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.96,0:14:33.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说实话  应该倒打一耙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:33.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, I think we should counter sue
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把痞老板所有财产都告过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for everything Plankton owns
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.92,0:14:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事情常有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that happen a lot?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有  一般是银的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, they're usually silver
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.27,0:14:46.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:46.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你先听听我的证词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you might want to hear my testimony
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你叫我出庭作证  我就会上去念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for when you call me as a character witness?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在排练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been rehearsing it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用你来提供证词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we won't be needing any testimony from you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉你比较会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you'd be more of a
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惹麻烦  没多大用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of a liability than an asset
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, run along--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶紧去准备庆功了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,make things shipshape for my victory celebration
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得早点去法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to get to the courthouse early
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费停船位就那么几个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:07.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only a few free parking places
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,官司一定胜券在握
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be a slam dunk
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:13.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板的律师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs's lawyer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:15.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Speak to me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摔疼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wracked with pain
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没法动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't move
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可蟹老板的官司怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what about Mr. Krabs's case?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你得亲自解决了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're going to have to handle this one, son
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I'm a
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惹麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a liability
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打赢官司的所有材料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:28.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything you need to win
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都在这箱子里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is in this here case
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.35,0:15:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有材料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:33.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只缺一件西装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.36,0:15:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything but a suit
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,西装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A suit
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.28,0:15:38.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道西装得上哪找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:38.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wonder where I could get a suit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,194)}法院
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.03,0:15:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再给你最后一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll give you one last chance
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.60,0:15:52.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,交出秘方就撤诉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:52.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll drop the charges if you give me the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想  你这小东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never, you little whelp
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的小胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My wittle arm
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.02,0:15:59.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:15:59.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.55,0:16:02.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我根本就没对他动爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:02.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't lay a claw on him
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我另一条胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:05.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My other arm
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:07.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's lying
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保持法庭肃静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Court will come to order
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挠背大法官主审
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Honorable Judge Tickleback presiding
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你的律师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, where is your attorney?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道他在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know where he could be
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I am
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢你入场  请问你是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for joining us, Mister
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵律师宝宝  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob Lawyerpants, Your Honor
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.26,0:16:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来干什么  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的律师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your lawyer, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,工作期间摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,fell down on the job
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过请蟹老板放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切都在我掌控之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have everything under control
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:33.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all in here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.26,0:16:34.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:34.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  就在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, right in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.00,0:16:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的律师没给我密码
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your lawyer didn't give me the combination
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原告是否准备好继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is the plaintiff ready to proceed?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Honor
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.44,0:16:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身为原生动物  并不总会饱受折磨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't always the tortured shell of a protozoa
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是今天却在你们面前痛苦挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that writhes in pain before you today
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.35,0:16:59.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:16:59.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,曾是个逍遥自在的单细胞生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:05.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was a vibrant carefree, happy-go-lucky single cell
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打起精神来  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就在那个命途多舛的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then came the fateful day
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.46,0:17:16.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我心中毫无恶意  去了那个死亡陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:16.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that I paid an innocent visit to the deathtrap
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,known as the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么样了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it coming, lad?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在开了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:21.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on the case
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正当我进了方才所说的那家店之时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Upon entering said establishment
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,周围没有告示  也毫无预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found myself without any warning
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.10,0:17:33.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我滑了一跤  摔在坚硬无情的地板上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,slipping and finally falling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,onto a hard, unforgiving floor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.19,0:17:37.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而地上还故意倒了滩罪孽深重的液体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that had been intentionally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:37.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,covered with a vicious fluid
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,投弹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:39.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bombs away
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你闹完了没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you quite finished?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚说到哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where was I?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最糟糕的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the worst part is
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来梦想要跑完马拉松的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my dreams of completing a marathon
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还跟我奶奶发过誓的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like I promised my old Grammy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,结果全都破灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have been dashed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Gram-Gram
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家关心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:10.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your kind attention
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.88,0:18:11.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:11.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被告是否进行开场陈述
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does the defense have an opening statement?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Honor
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奶奶好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:18.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor Gram-Gram
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你认得这个东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:21.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, can you identify this item?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(760,264)}小心地滑
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是小心地滑警告牌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a "Wet Floor" sign
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you own one?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1160,300)}陪审团
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  你们不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, you don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得做出艰难的商业决定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I had to make some tough business decisions
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.15,0:18:36.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这牌子好像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:36.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the sign seemed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很没必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,superfluous
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有其他问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more questions
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你举证  律师宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your witness, Mr. Lawyerpants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天之内举证  宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometime today, Mr. Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪审团的女士先生及庭上  请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May it please the court
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ladies and gentlemen of the jury
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大众称我的委托人小气  吝啬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my client has been called "cheap," "miserly,"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且长期抠门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and "chronically tightfisted"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但倘若他真如原告所言那般小气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:19:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But if he were as cheap as the prosecution claims he is
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他真的会眼睁睁的坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would he be able to sit there quietly
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我拿出一块钱  扔进搅拌机里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,while I took out a dollar and dropped it in the blender?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,402)}轻搅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(892,522)}重搅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:09.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1168,666)}狂搅
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy's got you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.17,0:19:16.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy's here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点胶水  一点胶带
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little glue, a little tape--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就能康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll be right as rain
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸没忘记你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy didn't forget you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被告是否申请证人出庭作证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does the defense have any witness to call?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.47,0:19:31.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Honor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被告申请
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:32.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Defense calls
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥出庭作证
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward to the stand
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.49,0:19:38.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  忠诚的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:38.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, a loyal employee
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mister, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大众称我的委托人小气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:42.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My client has been called "cheap"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否认可以上荒谬的陈述
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you agree with that ludicrous statement?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.03,0:19:45.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:45.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请允许我换个方式提问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:47.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to rephrase the question
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能否向庭上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you tell the court
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举例说明蟹老板有何大方表现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of some instance of Mr. Krabs's generosity in any way?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三年好不容易放一天假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One day off in three years
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非得过来作证吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I have to spend it testifying?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.08,0:20:03.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.08,0:20:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.85,0:20:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,open
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,case
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来  就是你害地板变滑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, it was you who made the floor slippery, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.65,0:20:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从实招来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Answer the question
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我提醒你  你可是宣过誓的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need I remind you you are under oath?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死到临头了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是别开箱子了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may as well give up on that case, me boy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my goose is cooked
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  你惊到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, I'm surprised at you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算事态不乐观也不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't give up just because things look bleak
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打赢官司得靠真心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This trial will be won by what's in your heart
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而不是这破箱子里的小玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not what's in this dumb old case
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's open
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.34,0:20:39.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:39.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是律师的午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:41.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just his lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被告申请痞老板出庭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Defense calls Plankton to the stand
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那天为什么要进蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:54.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why did you go into the Krusty Krab that day?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就  跟我从前的好朋友蟹老板打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To, you know, say hello to my once-good-friend, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.68,0:20:59.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:20:59.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定自己不是想去偷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it wasn't to make off
Dialogue: 1,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with one of these?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会是过去偷秘方的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:10.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Weren't you there to steal the formula
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.94,0:21:14.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好让你做出最香最好吃的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:14.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the most delicious, sweet-smelling sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村都远近闻名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,known to Bikini Bottom?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.76,0:21:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.76,0:21:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.61,0:21:33.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yippee
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally it's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take that
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.62,0:21:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  生命中最甜美的胜利再度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once again, Plankton, the sweetest of life's joys
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.12,0:21:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离你而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,has eluded your grasp
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陪审团是否已作出裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:54.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Has the jury reached a verdict?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  法官大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.04,0:21:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We have, Your Honor
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们裁决被告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.45,0:21:57.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We find the defendant
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.17,0:21:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not guilty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是很小气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.15,0:22:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he is cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.77,0:22:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一开始不让你帮忙  真有点糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:03.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was foolish not to accept
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your help from the beginning
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.10,0:22:05.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:05.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.66,0:22:06.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你做了礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:06.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made you a present
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的礼物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.88,0:22:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A present for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.02,0:22:12.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛  伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:12.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close your eyes and hold out your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,480)}小心地滑
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是小心地滑警告牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a "Wet Floor" sign
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.08,0:22:18.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我亲自做的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:18.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还算可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll do
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.33,0:22:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,毕竟免费
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.33,0:22:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,After all, it's free
